rows.label: tev060101_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Kupee if anything is troubling her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0001
rows.name: Welcome, traveler![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0002
rows.name:
This is Dopang Caravan, warm and caring home of
Nopon who prefer quiet, peaceful life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0003
rows.name:
Friend should rest now after long journey.
Caravan can be like second home to friend![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0004
rows.name:
...Oh, and if friend has any questions or problems,
just ask Kupee.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0005
rows.name:
Kupee take job as leader seriously and want friend
to feel taken care of.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0008
rows.name:
Hmm... Kupee does have troubles, but Kupee should
try to figure out solution alone first. ...Hrrrrrrg![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0009
rows.name:
...H-hrr-hrrrRRRRG! *gasp* *wheeze* *pant*
Meh-meh. Maybe Kupee thinking too hard.
Brain about to have meltdown![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0010
rows.name:
Maybe Kupee should just go ahead and ask friend for
help instead...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Kupee about Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Kupee about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_SEL1031
rows.name:
Ask Kupee about the humans
who have come to Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_SEL1041
rows.name:
Ask Kupee about the humans
who have come to Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0011
rows.name: Friend sees big round thing floating up there?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0012
rows.name: That is mystic place called noctilucent sphere![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0013
rows.name:
Very shiny and sparkling inside, although friend might
not be able to get there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0014
rows.name:
No roads lead to it, so friend will just have to learn
how to fly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0015
rows.name:
Too bad friend does not have wings like Kupee!
Then friend could flappity-flap right up there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0018
rows.name:
For some reason, Mira attracting awful lot of aliens
lately.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0019
rows.name:
There are human friends, Ganglion, and Mysteroids.
...Er, Kupee probably forgetting some others.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0020
rows.name:
There might even be secret aliens Kupee not meet yet!
Friend never knows.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0021
rows.name:
Anyway, so long as aliens here, Kupee hope they
enjoy time on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0022
rows.name:
Kupee make sure all aliens treated right and get help
they need at Dopang Caravan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0030
rows.name:
Kupee recently see lots of human friends congregating
near Shivering Sands.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0032
rows.name: Kupee warn friends that vicious Prone patrol area.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0033
rows.name: Sylvalum is very beautiful, but also full of danger.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0034
rows.name:
Worst when haze sets in and friends cannot see where
they are going. So be careful![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0039
rows.name:
Kupee heard sad news about human friends
congregating near Shivering Sands.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0040
rows.name: Apparently Prone did them all in. So sad![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0041
rows.name:
Also, human friends got turned into weapons!
Prone really are stupid jerkfaces...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0042
rows.name:
Prone probably turn Nopon they catch into cushions
and sit on them until stuffing is squished out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0043
rows.name: See big round thing floating up there?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0044
rows.name:
That is mystic place called noctilucent sphere.
Kupee love it there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0045
rows.name:
Kupee had not been for while, but other day decided
to pop in and have little bit of chill time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0046
rows.name:
Bad idea! Monster called Pharsis, the Everqueen
move in and strut around like she own place!
Kupee not get any chill time at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG0047
rows.name:
If Everqueen was even just a little bit adorable,
Kupee might have tried to make friends. But nope![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Kupee about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG2001
rows.name:
Lots of Nopon say such bad things about Elder Nan.
How elder is spoiled... Or coward... Or total pervert...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG2002
rows.name: But Kupee know elder is thinking about Nopon future![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG2003
rows.name:
Elder only tell Nopon to move to New LA to protect
them from mean and dangerous Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060101_MSG2004
rows.name:
But Kupee has to stay with caravan great Dopang
passed down to her instead of heading into city,
which is kind of scary.[ST:wait ]
